channel.title: Most Basic Downloadable Source?
channel.description:
OK, I'm Going To Try To Make This Pretty Clear I'm Going To Make An Entirely New Server. Does Anyone Know Of A Silabsoft Source That Doesn't Have A Lot Of Things Added To It? I'm Just Going To Go Through It, Delete All The NPCs, Get Rid Of The Standard Quests, Etc., Then Fully Customize It So It Is Entirely Original.
I Know That So Far All I've Done Is Ask Questions, But I Want To Get Everything Right So I Don't Screw Something Up Or Get Stuck With A Days Worth Of Work Just Deleting Pointless Objects And Voids.
